.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family, time-travel, fantasy, adventure, thriller, disaster
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, ship, train, trike
 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the person driving the bus is the person watching family movies##1
13. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
14. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | disaster      | fantasy     | martial-arts  | adventure | time-travel | family |
