.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk, tea, water
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, engineer, journalist, manager, musician, photographer
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, goat, guinea-pig, lizard, bird, horse
 1. the owner of the mouse is the accountant##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is the journalist##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the owner of the goat is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the horse and the photographer##2
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the owner of the mouse is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the owner of the horse is the person drinking water##1
15. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | coffee     | soy-milk   | tea        | fanta   | iced-tea     | milk     | water    |
