 9. the teacher is between the person playing snooker and the person playing whist##2
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person playing billiard##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person playing go##1
12. the dancer is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
14. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

