.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, house, metal, punk, reggae, salsa, trance
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony, azure, pink, white, apricot, coral
 1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is between the fan of reggae and the fan of metal##2
 3. the fan of d&b is the person who likes ebony##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the fan of d&b is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the person who likes ebony##1
10. the writer is the person who likes white##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
14. the fan of house is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
