 2. the person driving the trike is the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing go##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
